{"tid":1365213,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大家一齊捉緊7月嘅尾巴去睇向日葵花海","createTime":"2019-07-25T14:40:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T16:07:27.000Z","uid":27715,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f1e7c98bccbe28e4787a26f5db69b141b1ca6742","tid":1365213,"uid":27715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:40:31.000Z","msg":"唔知大家對向日葵花海有冇興趣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UZx8TPh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUZx8TPh.png&h=c912c978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n知道連登多學生哥，學生嘅錢有限，暑假機票又貴，冇錢飛去日本睇向日葵花海<br />\n不過唔緊要！！！！！！<br />\n原來香港都有得睇啊！！！！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">地址：元朗新田信芯園2019</span><br />\n開放時間：星期一至日08:00-（預計開放至7月尾）18:00<br />\n交通資訊：信芯園交通於新元朗中心乘巴士76K或紅色小巴17號，在石湖圍下車後沿水管步行於港鐵錦上路站乘綠色小巴78號，在石湖圍下車後沿水管步行於港鐵元朗站坐的士直入小磡村信芯園，約$ 80，視乎交通情況而定<br />\n<br />\n另外有啲衣著小建議想比入去影靚相打卡嘅各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以戴翻頂黃色嘅帽 襯翻啲黃色嘅向日葵花花<br />\n示意圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZOooHCv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZOooHCv.png&h=de459858&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">*記住遵守秩序，影相個陣大家都要愛護大自然，千祈唔好破壞咁靚嘅向日葵花田，唔好亂踩啊！<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">各位，我想係到招下model，想大家幫我完成份VA SBA，需要好多好多人27號係元朗，戴住黃色帽一齊入信芯園做model比我影相，不過我冇錢比你，無飯派架，仲可能會受傷添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"5e51fdcff093649bcafeac56c7dad14d48adff79","tid":1365213,"uid":27715,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:43:25.000Z","msg":"小妹需要大家嘅幫手去完成份SBA啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c279a692aed7a0b189236d54b2dc9fe4cb8c05","tid":1365213,"uid":27715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:44:02.000Z","msg":"希望727元朗見到大家肯做我嘅model!!!"},{"pid":"d8059987ac61bb79231b31cd99ba6dfd420804e1","tid":1365213,"uid":27715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:44:23.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"7bc908c2bb5d0f508895e24995e8256c2e301f4f","tid":1365213,"uid":91154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:45:59.000Z","msg":"好想做model<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb3eeab3cd9483eaa48ff0a5e3b92efdd577182","tid":1365213,"uid":281282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:46:35.000Z","msg":"Good!"},{"pid":"f18793faf96ddde82ccbfedacf0eb7ee1ace1fc6","tid":1365213,"uid":275723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:48:48.000Z","msg":"Push, 打卡一流 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff42a7d5871f948ef78e0681ae5701a8d559363","tid":1365213,"uid":27715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bc908c2bb5d0f508895e24995e8256c2e301f4f","tid":1365213,"uid":91154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:45:59.000Z","msg":"好想做model<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:49:39.000Z","msg":"嚟啦嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有眼耳口鼻就做得！"},{"pid":"bb0f4b5a7b1c767427e66a36f9b9523990ac7fdf","tid":1365213,"uid":27715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fb3eeab3cd9483eaa48ff0a5e3b92efdd577182","tid":1365213,"uid":281282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:46:35.000Z","msg":"Good!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c725c0c47d8da7a66eace8fff2b7b0